                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_9549">Minhaj al-Yaqin.</title>
                     <note>F1a: a) Impression of rectangular seal of ... Ibn Murtada 'Ali, dated A.H.1214. b) Partly effaced note with name Mahmud, not the author, presumably an owner. F1b: Impression of small oval seal of Muhammad Salim, date A.H. 1117, regnal year 51 (of Aurangzeb). Currently held in an envelope with a pencilled note by Simon Digby on it, dated June 1975. A commentary on the Testament of the Imam Ja'far al-Sadiq. Headings and punctuation in red.</note>
                     <incipit>Rawa'ih-i ... 'adil sar-garm</incipit>
                     <listBibl>
